{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 151 "Notice this is a lot closer than was lef
tsum using only 7 boxes.  Let's use the average of the leftbox and rig
htbox idea.  In other words we will use  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "(area of th
e leftbox + the area of the right box)/2" "6#*&,&**%%areaG\"\"\"%#ofGF
'%$theGF'%(leftboxGF'F'*.F)F'F&F'F(F'F)F'%&rightGF'%$boxGF'F'F'\"\"#!
\"\"" }{TEXT -1 3 ".  " }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 101 "(
leftsum(f,x=-4..2,7)+rightsum(f,x=-4..2,7))/2=value((leftsum(f,x=-4..2
,7)+rightsum(f,x=-4..2,7))/2);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#/,&*
