0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 163 "This is pretty clos
e.  I seem to recall that the average of the leftbox area and the righ
tbox area is the area of the obvious trapezoid. Try the trapezoid comm
and." }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 53 "trapezoid(f,x=-4..2,
